      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CRITICAL MOMENT (1) ran below his best last time finishing fourth (30.01) over 520m at Wentworth Park in a Grade 5. Form at the trip excellent including five wins. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Can discover winning form. DESPICABLE KYRO (5) bolted home by 5 lengths (22.29) at this track last time from box 1. Will need some luck early after drawing a tricky box here. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Deserves serious consideration again. WRECK IT REX (7) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 2 lengths at The Gardens in a handy 22.98 beating Rie Bale. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Expected to measure up again. FASCINATE BAILEY (2) looks an each-way chance.",
